(18, 'Why Commercial Cleaning Companies Are Worth the Investment', 'Why Commercial Cleaning Companies Are Worth the Investment', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: poppinsregular, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.28px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400;\">It is important to keep a workplace clean for the comfort and motivation of employees. A healthy workspace should be free from distractions and provide a good environment in which to work. However, with the speed and pace of business these days, it can be difficult to bring the needed standard in office hygiene. Hence, a big benefit for organisations is the availability of commercial cleaning services that suit beyond the provision of in-house cleaning teams.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: poppinsregular, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.28px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400;\">If you have been wondering whether to hire professional cleaning services, let us assure you: such services are very much worth the budget. Why all kinds of enterprises should go to<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://cqdcleaningservices.com/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(16, 92, 127); text-decoration: none; transition: 0.4s ease-out;\">commercial cleaning companies</a><span>&nbsp;</span>and how their services can upgrade your workspace.</span></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: poppins_mediumregular; font-weight: 500; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(11, 53, 76); margin: 20px 0px; font-size: 26px; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: -0.03em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400;\">Real Cost of a Clean Workplace</span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: poppinsregular, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.28px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400;\">Most businesses have their employees or a small cleaning team do the routine cleaning, ignoring the chances that this might incur hidden costs. Employee productivity, well-being, or morale could decline if an employee would rather be doing something else than take time for cleaning.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px; colo