r-box;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: poppins_mediumregular; font-weight: 500; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(11, 53, 76); margin: 20px 0px; font-size: 26px; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: -0.03em;\">1. Collect empty glasses, plates etc.</h2></div></div><div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px;\">Make sure to collect any empty glasses and plates from tables quickly and safely. We would recommend sanitising your hands before and after as well to ensure maximum safety.</p></div></div><div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: poppins_mediumregular; font-weight: 500; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(11, 53, 76); margin: 20px 0px; font-size: 26px; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: -0.03em;\">2. Wipe down surfaces</h2></div></div><div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px;\">During your shift, you need to ensure that surfaces are being regularly wiped down with antibacterial cleaner. This means sanitising and wiping down tables between customers and regularly cleaning surfaces throughout the premises, especially in places like bathrooms. Whilst most guests will remain seated throughout their visit, when they venture to the toilet they might touch more areas than anticipated. Therefore, it is a good idea to be well prepared and wipe down all surfaces regularly.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e8afb87 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con\" data-id=\"e8afb87\" data-element_typ